      "text": "サニピに入る前は、事務所の業務を手伝って\nいたんですよね？",
      "startTime": 237.366642674,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな。遙子さんは昔から気遣いの出来る人で\n俺もよく助けてもらっていたよ",
      "startTime": 242.9999780419,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "事務処理や書類の作成を手伝ってくれたり\n電話番をしてくれたり、お茶を淹れてくれたり……",
      "startTime": 248.4666447086,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 11233.336090899997,
          "startTime": 259.6999807995
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-rei022.m4a",
      "text": "お茶ですね！　それなら私にも出来ます\nすぐに淹れてくるので、ちょっと待ってて下さい",
      "startTime": 256.0999780419,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、おい、怜！？　行ってしまった……\nまぁ、自主練でもして無理されるよりはいいか",
      "startTime": 264.3999475243,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5666.710114300031,
          "startTime": 270.0666576386
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cup-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10700.060613800018,
          "startTime": 275.1000081381
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
