      "text": "お待たせしました。粗茶ですが、どうぞ",
      "startTime": 271.4919164984,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "会社のものを粗茶って言うのはどうかと思うが……\nありがとう。遠慮なくいただくよ",
      "startTime": 279.8999312484,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
