      "text": "えっ？　ちょっと失礼します\n……うぅっ、確かに濃過ぎますね",
      "startTime": 296.233325617,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-rei025.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、茶葉を入れ過ぎたみたいです\nすぐ淹れ直します",
      "startTime": 305.5000044906,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "いや、いいよ。このままでも飲めるから\n気にしないで怜はその辺でくつろいでいてくれ",
      "startTime": 310.4000004217,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-rei026.m4a",
      "text": "……いえ、失敗したまま終わる訳にはいきません\n私に名誉挽回のチャンスを下さい！",
      "startTime": 318.4333195135,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-rei027.m4a",
      "text": "他に手伝えることはありませんか？\nなんでも遠慮なく言って下さい！",
      "startTime": 325.4333195135,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-koh018.m4a",
      "text": "いや、こんなところで負けん気を発揮しなくても……\nやってほしいことも、今はないし……",
      "startTime": 331.5999821112,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-rei028.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、遙子さんに手伝ってもらって\n嬉しかったことは何かありませんか！？",
      "startTime": 338.0333195136,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-rei029.m4a",
      "text": "教えてくれたら私もそれをやります！",
      "startTime": 341.427167242,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-koh019.m4a",
      "text": "嬉しかったこと？　そうだな……小腹が空いた時に\n遙子さんがおにぎりを作ってくれたことがあったが……",
      "startTime": 350.6666528469,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
