      "text": "お待たせしました！　給湯室にあった土鍋で\nお米を炊いておにぎりにしました。食べてみて下さい！",
      "startTime": 368.0334436184,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-koh020.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ありがとう。いただきます",
      "startTime": 373.0357490077,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-koh021.m4a",
      "text": "うっ！　硬い……このお米、芯が残ってるぞ\nお米を炊くのに失敗したみたいだな",
      "startTime": 383.5334436184,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-rei032.m4a",
      "text": "えっ！？　す、すみません……\nお茶もろくに淹れられないし、おにぎりも作れない……",
      "startTime": 392.2334273423,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-rei033.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり私じゃ、遙子さんのようには\n出来ないんですね……",
      "startTime": 401.100094009,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-koh022.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに落ち込まなくてもいいんじゃないか？\nお茶を淹れることとアイドルは関係ないんだから",
      "startTime": 405.200073664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-rei034.m4a",
      "text": "その関係ないことを\n遙子さんはずっと続けていたんですよね……",
      "startTime": 410.8333947903,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-rei035.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルとして売れていなかった時期も、成功するため\n諦めず地道にコツコツ活動を続けて……",
      "startTime": 419.0667281236,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-rei036.m4a",
      "text": "もし私だったら我慢出来ずに、もっと練習したいとか\nもっと仕事がほしいとか無理を言って困らせてたかも",
      "startTime": 428.0333947903,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-rei037.m4a",
      "text": "私は早く結果がほしくて、焦って失敗してばかり……\nもっと遙子さんみたいに、落ち着きを持たないと",
      "startTime": 440.1333846177,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
